un.com|publisher=}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[James Kelleher]]\n|\n|\n|\n| former member of the [[Senate of Canada]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/information/about/process/senate/annualrep/0506/annexes-e.html|title=The Senate of Canada Annual Report 2005\u20132006|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.radissonmining.com/company/management.html|title=Oups! La page recherch\u00e9e n'existe pas|first=Radisson|last=Mining|publisher=}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Peter Kormos]] \n|\n|\n|\n| former Minister of Consumer and Commercial Relations, [[House Leader]] for the Ontario NDP Caucus<ref>{{cite web|url=https://niagaraatlarge.com/2010/10/28/niagara%e2%80%99s-peter-kormos-slams-ontario-government-for-slapping-harmonized-sales-tax-on-remembrance-day-poppies/|title=Niagara's Peter Kormos Slams Ontario Government For Slapping Harmonized Sales Tax on Remembrance Day Poppies|date=28 October 2010|publisher=}}</ref><ref>http://ontariondp.com/node/565/print</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Zahir Lalani]] \n|\n|\n|\n| Consul and Senior Representative for New York at the [[Bank of Canada]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bank-banque-canada.ca/en/bios/lalani.html|title=Bank of Canada \u2013 Banque du Canada|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.arnetminer.net/viewuniversity.do?keyword=University%20of%20York|title=AMiner|first=Yutao|last=Zhang|publisher=arnetminer.net}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Floyd Laughren]] \n|\n|\n|\n| former Ontario NDP MPP and finance minister<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.citizensassembly.gov.on.ca/gallery1/en/LearningWeekend2.html|title=Citizens' Assembly on Electoral Reform|publisher=}}</ref><ref>http://www.yorku.ca/cdis/bursaries.pdf</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Jack Layton]] \n|\n|\n|\n| Leader of the federal [[New Democratic Party of Canada|New Democratic Party]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ndp.ca/jacklayton|title=Canada's NDP|publisher=}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[William Ross Macdonald]] \n|\n|\n|\n| fo