anna|title=Who is Supreme Court Justice Asher Dan Grunis?|url=http://www.jpost.com/NationalNews/Article.aspx?id=247371|accessdate=26 August 2012|newspaper=The Jerusalem Post|date=29 November 2011}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Frank Joseph Hughes]] \n| Supreme Court Judge<ref>http://www.scc-csc.gc.ca/court-cour/ju/hughes/index-eng.asp</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Wilfred Judson]] \n| former puisne judge of the Supreme Court of Canada<ref>http://scc.lexum.umontreal.ca/fr/bulletin/2004/04-10-22-bul.wpd/04-10-22-bul.wpd.html</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Patrick Kerwin]] \n| former [[Chief Justice of Canada]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scc-csc.gc.ca/court-cour/ju/kerwin/index-eng.asp |title=Archived copy |access-date=2011-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101012024048/http://www.scc-csc.gc.ca/court-cour/ju/kerwin/index-eng.asp |archive-date=2010-10-12 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Harry S. Laforme]] \n| Ont. Court of Appeal, head of Aboriginal Truth and Reconciliation Commission of Canada<ref>http://osgoode.yorku.ca/media2.nsf/releases/EAF63AC68D572C8D85256F54007E23E0</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Bora Laskin]] \n| former Chief Justice of Canada<ref>http://www.osgoodesociety.ca/books/book-20053.html</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Claire L'Heureux-Dube]]\n| former judge of the Supreme Court of Canada (LLD)<ref>http://osgoode.yorku.ca/osgmedia.nsf/research/mossman_mary_jane</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Patrick LeSage]]\n| former Chief Justice of Ontario<ref>http://osgoode.yorku.ca/media2.nsf/releases/9F45A6D64791B8D08525754300554AF0</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Allen Linden]] \n| Federal Court of Appeal judge<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fca-caf.gc.ca/about/bios/linden_e.shtml |title=Archived copy |access-date=2011-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070726233710/http://www.fca-caf.gc.ca/about/bios/linden_e.shtml |archive-date=2007-07-26 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Goldwyn Arthur Martin]]\n| [