c-professor-named-to-order-of-canada/|title=York University music professor named to Order of Canada|last=InsideToronto.com|publisher=}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Ali Kazimi]] \n| filmmaker\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Ruth Koleszar-Green]] \n| Professor of Social Work, Indigenous activist\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Gabriel Kolko]] \n| Professor Emeritus of History\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Bonita Lawrence]]\n|Associate Professor, Department of Equity Studies, Indigenous rights activist\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Irving Layton]] \n| poet\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Jack Layton]] \n| leader of the [[New Democratic Party of Canada|New Democratic Party]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[James Laxer]] \n| author, columnist and commentator, Professor of Canadian Politics\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Lee Lorch]] \n| Professor Emeritus of Mathematics, civil rights activist, member of [[Cuban Academy of Sciences]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Edelgard Mahant]]\n| political science\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[David T. McNab]]\n| M\u00e9tis historian\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Patrick J. Monahan]] \n| Professor of Law\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Heather Monroe-Blum]]\n| current Principal and Vice-Chancellor of [[McGill University]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Jonathan Nitzan]] \n| Professor of Political Economy\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[David F. Noble]] \n| Historian of Technology\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Michael Ondaatje]] \n| author and filmmaker, Professor of English Literature\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Leo Panitch]] \n| Distinguished Research Professor of Political Science (Canada Research Chair in Political Economy), editor of the [[Socialist Register]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Andreas Papandreou]] \n| Greek Prime Minister, Economics Professor (1969\u20131974)\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[William Phillips (economist)|William Phillips]]\n| Professor of Economics, notable for his contribution in economics with the [[Phillips Curve]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Joseph Pivato]]\n| Visiting Professor, Mariano Elia Chair in Italian-Canad