ot_record_detail&fl=0&lg=English&ex=00000392&rd=98253&alt=Premier+John+Robarts&hs=1</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://penguinrandomhouse.ca/search/title|title=Search|publisher=}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Lisa Raitt]] \n|\n|\n|\n| Canadian Minister of Natural Resources<ref>http://pm.gc.ca/eng/bio.asp?id=85</ref><ref>http://osgoode.yorku.ca/media2.nsf/5457ed39bc56dbfd852571e900728656/3e7a4d53fd634658852574f600562070?OpenDocument</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Ian Scott (Ontario politician)|Ian Scott]] \n|\n|\n|\n| former Attorney General of Ontario<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/former-ontario-attorney-general-ian-scott-dies-1.598532 | work=CBC News | title=Former Ontario attorney general Ian Scott dies | date=2006-10-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theinquiry.ca/Ian_Scott.hide.php|title=The Inquiry \u2013 Cornwall Ontario sex abuse scandal|publisher=}}</ref>\n|-\n|Ulric Shannon\n|\n|\n|\n|Consul General of Canada in Istanbul, Turkey<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.canada.ca/en/global-affairs/news/2016/07/biographical-notes.html|title=Biographical notes \u2013 Canada.ca|last=Canada|first=Global Affairs|website=www.canada.ca|language=en|access-date=2017-09-24}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|[[Jagmeet Singh]]\n|\n|\n|\n|Leader of the Federal [[New Democratic Party]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Karen Kraft Sloan]] \n|\n|\n|\n| former [[United Nations]] Ambassador of the environment<ref>https://www.un.org/esa/sustdev/csd/csd14/statements/canada_12may.pdf</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uwinnipeg.ca/index/quest-bio-kraftsloan|title=UW-|publisher=}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Greg Sorbara]] \n|\n|\n|\n| [[Ontario Minister of Finance]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gregsorbara.com/|title=Greg Sorbara \u2013 The Battlefield of Ontario Politics|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gregsorbara.com/bio.aspx?id=biography|title=Page not found \u2013 Greg Sorbara|publisher=}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[John Tory]] \n|\n|\n|\n| 