ynaptics]]</ref>{{Circular reference|date=May 2019}}\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Isabel Bassett]] \n| former [[Member of Provincial Parliament (Ontario)|MPP]] and [[chief executive officer]] of [[TVOntario]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| Sir [[Edward Wentworth Beatty]]\n| President of the [[Canadian Pacific Railway]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Douglas G. Bergeron]] \n| billionaire, President and CEO of [[Verifone]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[George Butterfield (businessman)|George Butterfield]] \n| co-founder of luxury active travel company Butterfield & Robinson\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Ivan Fecan]] \n| President and [[chief executive officer]], [[CTV Television Network|CTV]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| Dennis Fotinos\n| President and CEO of [[Enwave]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| Robert J. Gemmell\n| former President and CEO of [[Citigroup]] Global Markets Canada Inc.\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Alexander Haditaghi]] \n| founder, owner and chairman of Pacific Mortgage Company, CEO of MoPals.com\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| John S. Hunkin\n| former CEO of [[Canadian Imperial Bank of Commerce|CIBC]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| Colleen Johnston\n| Group Head Finance and Chief Financial Officer at [[TD Bank Financial Group]]<ref>{{cite web\n|url = http://www.americanbanker.com/usb_issues/119_10/colleen_johnston-1002059-1.html\n|title = #21 Colleen Johnston\n|publisher = US Banker\n|accessdate = 2010-01-11}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Vikas Kohli]]\n| Founder of [[Fatlabs]] [[Recording Studio]] in Mississauga, Ontario, Canada\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Gordon Lownds]] \n| co-founder of [[Sleep Country Canada]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Sergio Marchionne]] \n| President and CEO of [[Fiat]] and [[Chrysler]] Group LLC\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Rob McEwen]] \n| President and CEO of [[US Gold Corporation]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| Alan G. McNally\n| former Chairman of [[Harris Bank]]\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| Eileen Mercier\n| Chair of [[Ontario Teachers' Pension Plan]] Board\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Larry Organ]] \n| Chief Executive