rds-and-recognition/university-professors/ \"University Professor\"]</ref> are the highest ranks a professor can achieve at York University. There are a maximum of 25 active Distinguished Research Professors and active University Professors at any time.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://secretariat-policies.info.yorku.ca/policies/honorific-professorships/ |title=Honorific Professorships|website=secretariat-policies.info.yorku.ca}}</ref> It is awarded to members of the faculty who have made outstanding contributions to the University through their work in research.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://vpap.info.yorku.ca/awards-and-recognition/distinguished-research-professors|title=Vice-President Academic and Provost|website=vpap.info.yorku.ca}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width: 100%;\"\n! width = \"25%\" | Name\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Year of award & notability \n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Pat Armstrong]]\n| 2010: Sociology, Liberal Arts & Professional Studies\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Gerald O. Aspirall]]\n| 1988: Chemistry, Science\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Isabella C. Bakker]]\n| 2014: Political Science, Liberal Arts & Professional Studies\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Norbert Bartel]]\n| 2006: Physics & Astronomy, Science & Engineering\n|-\n|[[Dawn Bazely]]<ref>[http://dawnbazely.lab.yorku.ca/ Dawn Bazely]</ref>\n|2017:  Biology, Science<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://yfile.news.yorku.ca/2017/06/18/professor-dawn-bazely-to-receive-the-title-of-university-professor-during-spring-convocation/|title=Professor Dawn Bazely to receive the title of University Professor during spring convocation \u2013 YFile|website=yfile.news.yorku.ca|language=en-CA|access-date=2017-10-26}}</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Russell Belk]]\n| 2014: Schulich School of Business\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Ellen Bialystok]]\n| 2003: Psychology, Arts\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[Diethard Bohme]]\n| 1995: Chemistry, Pure & Applied Science\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| [[John Bosher]]\n| 1989: History, Arts\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|